# 🐰 Project: Funny Rabbits  
### 🔹 Description (English)

**Funny Rabbits** is one of my early web design projects, where I first learned how HTML builds the structure of a webpage.  
After completing the main HTML part, **today I started my very first step into CSS.**  
I haven’t learned all the details yet — I’m just exploring what CSS can do and how it changes the look of a page.

Even though the project is still simple, I can already see how style and design can make a big difference.  
This step made me even more excited to keep learning.

### 💡 What I Learned:
- Reviewing HTML helped me understand the importance of clean structure  
- I learned what CSS is used for and how it works beside HTML  
- Every small progress counts — and I’m proud of each step  

This project is still in progress, and I’ll keep updating it as I learn more about web design.

